#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:28
msgid "Quickstart"
msgstr "快速入门"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:30
msgid ""
"Welcome to Ghostwriter! This platform streamlines security assessment "
"reporting and team collaboration."
msgstr "欢迎使用 Ghostwriter！本平台用于简化安全评估报告流程与团队协作。"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:32
msgid "Ghostwriter helps you manage the entire assessment lifecycle through:"
msgstr "Ghostwriter 通过以下功能协助管理评估全生命周期："

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:34
msgid "Client management and project tracking"
msgstr "客户管理与项目跟踪"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:35
msgid "Findings library with reusable content"
msgstr "可复用内容的发现项库"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:36
msgid "Infrastructure tracking for assessments"
msgstr "评估基础设施跟踪"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:37
msgid "Report generation and collaboration with customizable templates"
msgstr "基于自定义模板的报告生成与协作"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:40
msgid "To get started:"
msgstr "开始使用："

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:42
msgid "Explore existing clients and projects via the sidebar"
msgstr "通过侧边栏浏览已有客户与项目"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:43
msgid "Set your active report to track your current work"
msgstr "设置当前报告以跟踪正在进行的工作"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:44
msgid "Add findings to your report from the library or create custom ones"
msgstr "从库中添加发现项到报告，或创建自定义条目"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:45
msgid "Generate reports with consistent formatting"
msgstr "生成格式统一的报告"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:48
msgid ""
"Use the sidebar navigation to access all features. This dashboard will show "
"your assignments and project calendar events to keep you organized."
msgstr "使用侧边栏导航访问所有功能。本仪表板会显示分配给你的任务与项目日历事件，便于统筹安排。"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:49
msgid ""
"If you don't see any clients or projects, you may need to create them or "
"request access. A manager or admin can assign you to an existing project to "
"get you started. Once you have a project and a report, you can easily access"
" them at any time from the left-hand sidebar available on every page."
msgstr ""
"若未显示任何客户或项目，可能需要创建或申请访问权限。管理员可将你加入已有项目以便开始工作。获得项目和报告后，可随时通过每个页面左侧的侧边栏快速访问。"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:51
msgid ""
"Learn more from the <a href=\"https://ghostwriter.wiki/\" class=\"dashboard-"
"link\">Ghostwriter Wiki</a>. Join our <a href=\"https://ghst.ly/BHSlack\" "
"class=\"dashboard-link\">SpecterOps Slack Community</a> and the "
"<em>#ghostwriter</em> channel to discuss Ghostwriter, ask questions, and get"
" help."
msgstr ""
"更多信息请访问 <a href=\"https://ghostwriter.wiki/\" class=\"dashboard-"
"link\">Ghostwriter Wiki</a>。可加入 <a href=\"https://ghst.ly/BHSlack\" "
"class=\"dashboard-link\">SpecterOps Slack 社区</a> 的 <em>#ghostwriter</em> "
"频道交流、提问与获取帮助。"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:53
msgid "Don't Show This Again"
msgstr "不再显示"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:61
msgid "Ready to Work?"
msgstr "准备开始工作？"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:64
