msgstr "你已被分配到部分活跃项目，可在此查看："

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:73
msgid ""
"Open the sidebar on the left to view/manage your reports under <em>My Active"
" Reports</em>."
msgstr "打开左侧侧边栏，可在 <em>我的活跃报告</em> 中查看与管理报告。"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:74
msgid ""
"Select a report to mark it as active. If you're managing multiple reports, "
"you can switch your active reports from there, too."
msgstr "选择一份报告将其标记为活跃报告。若同时管理多份报告，也可在此切换当前活跃报告。"

#: ghostwriter/templates/index.html:76
